    "longBusinessSummary": "Petrovietnam Camau Fertilizer Corporation engages in the production and trading of fertilizers, nitrogen compounds, and basic chemicals in Vietnam. The company also engages in wholesale and retail of fertilizers, chemicals, and bioactive products used for industrial/agricultural uses; agricultural activities and consultancy; warehousing, storage, loading, and unloading services; research and development of natural science and engineering, technical testing, and analyzing; repair and maintenance of machinery and equipment; and website set-up and processing of rental data. In addition, it is involved in the trading of products and materials, plant varieties, agriculture products, and pesticides; production of non-alcoholic beverages and mineral water; real estate business with owned and leased property; supply and management of labor resources; and designing locations, presenting and implementing advertising on websites, application software for electronic devices, and handheld devices, as well as provision of fertilizing testing services. Further, then company exports its products. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Cà Mau, Vietnam. Petrovietnam Camau Fertilizer Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Vietnam Oil and Gas Group.",
